{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act28side", "eventName": "不義之財", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CV-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "孤獨之地", "storyInfo": "在山林中，一位年老的當地獵人從野獸口中救下了潔西卡，並帶她離開深林去往任務地點達維鎮。同時，小隊成員也正懷著對潔西卡的擔憂朝地塊行進。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "warp", "attributes": {"name": "chiyu01"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慌亂間，潔西卡摸向腰間的手銃，可恐懼讓她的手指搭在銃套上，遲遲無法彎曲。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她隱約從寒風中嗅到了一絲腥氣。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別亂動。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunshot", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fmalebstwhin", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.8, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位獵人從林中走進潔西卡的視線，他手裡的銃還在冒煙，寬大的帽檐遮住了眼睛。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她轉身再看向身後，一具野獸的屍體橫躺在雪地上，頭上的傷口還在汩汩地流著鮮血。"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡你該多留點神。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝您……救了我。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順手罷了。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人一邊收起銃，一邊徑直走向野獸的屍體。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knife", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他抽出小刀，破開野獸的腹部，角度精準，沒有多少血液流出。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，他將雙手塞入屍體腹內，發出一聲長長的嘆息。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這鬼天氣真是他媽冷得要死。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……老先生，您是附近的獵人嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您知道達維鎮該怎麼走嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你去那裡做什麼？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我打算在那裡和隊友會合。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是一個人來的？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我和隊友分頭行動，從一夥流寇手中營救了一名人質，但任務結束後我的通訊器意外損壞，在林子裡迷了路。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人質？長什麼樣子？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是位年老的豐蹄男性……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#14$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……居然是你們。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那好，跟我走吧。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去、去哪裡？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是要去達維鎮嗎？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來不來隨你便。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-20", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人沒再看潔西卡，起身將野獸屍體扛在肩上，快步向林子深處走去。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，等等！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-500,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，潔西卡一個人在外面，你真的放心嗎？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你擔心潔西卡，我也一樣。但是一起戰鬥這麼多年，我相信她有能力獨自處理好。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是不確定還會不會有殘餘的匪徒。兩三個倒沒問題，可萬一他們還有殘部呢？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#4$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡曾經歷過的戰鬥可比那些烏合之眾危險得多。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#4$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要嘛是箭簇貼著頭皮飛過，要嘛是利刃擦著喉嚨劃過。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#2$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再要不，四周全是高濃度的活性源石粉塵，防護服稍微裂開一個小小的口子，立刻就能在那裡升天。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#2$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但每一次她的任務都順利完成了，沒有我們的陪同，也不在我們的視線裡。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只有一個人，但什麼都做得非常好。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#9$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我不否認。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#4$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你也知道，每次任務完成，她都眼眶通紅地回來。在她回來見我們之前，哭得眼淚汪汪的時候，總得有個人在身邊吧？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#10$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通紅的眼眶代表什麼？代表她每次都是擦乾眼淚才來見我們，她不樂意別人見到她哭。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可她才二十三歲——", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#5$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，二十三歲，而且過去三年裡有兩年半都花在戰場上。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_treefrzrupture", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老先生，請問附近有什麼東西爆炸了嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_treefrzrupture", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowfall", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像又聽到了，就在附近……難道是我幻聽了？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是爆炸，是樹。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樹？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#16$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林子裡太冷，樹液凍結之後會膨脹，把樹幹裡的組織撐裂。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽起來……就像從遠處傳來的交火聲。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底是什麼人？軍隊，僱傭兵？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僱傭兵，差不多當了五年了。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你家裡欠債了？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……只是我……不想受家裡人的庇護，走家裡人為我安排好的道路……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你就去當傭兵？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是啊……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，那你在戰場上尋找什麼？財富、名聲，還是榮譽？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我要做的是排除危機，解決衝突，在險境中保護別人……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦……原來傭兵是幹這個的，我還是頭一回知道。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#8$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_treefrzrupture", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowfall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老先生……我們不是普通的傭兵公司，我們……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "42_g9_modernoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提醒你一句，潔西卡，你是傭兵，你的任務只是生意，不是義務。", "name": "“橋夾”克里夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1036_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，打住吧，我不關心那個。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-300,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打擾了二位，你們剛剛聊的人是位有五年實戰經歷的“資深”傭兵嗎？", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#1$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你有什麼見解要發表，小羅拉？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們和潔西卡共事的時間比我長，她的能力跟極限，你們應該比我更清楚，不是嗎？", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你覺得潔西卡自己能搞定？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。雷蛇隊長說得沒錯，過去三年裡，她去過的地方比這裡危險得多。", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#11$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然一想到潔西卡淚汪汪的樣子，我也會不由自主地擔心，但其實我們誰都知道，她沒問題的，不是嗎？", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了她自己不知道。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，只有她自己不知道……", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#3$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她可能就差那麼一個機會了，一個讓她看清自己的機會。", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道你想說現在就是那個機會？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#3$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……倒也不是……", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#8$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "d", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老、老先生……老先生！", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐，你有點吵。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我不是故意想吵您……但您能不能看看那裡……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潔西卡指向遠處樹旁的一處獸夾。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那裡，一隻幼獸的前腿被鋼夾緊緊咬住。幼獸不停地哀鳴，血從咬合處緩緩滲出。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老獵人看到後，放下野獸屍體，走到樹下解開捕獸夾，將幼獸從夾子裡取出。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是幼崽……或許我們可以把它放了。要是母獸在附近，應該很快就能找來……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，我聽說獵人冬天會放過母獸和幼崽，讓獸群得以繁衍……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它母親已經在這裡了。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您剛剛打死的那隻野獸是它的母親？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見過這隻帶崽的母獸好幾次。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，大的被打死了，小的不知踩在哪個冒失鬼放的夾子上，獸皮都壞了。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……我們現在該拿這隻幼獸怎麼辦？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擰斷它的脖子，給它一個痛快。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會？！", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然呢？沒了母親又斷了腿，它馬上就死了。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者你也可以把它留在這裡慢慢咽氣，我也沒意見。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……它沒法活下去，是嗎？", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請您把它給我吧……", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要自己動手？請便。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-20", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓……沒事了，小傢伙……沒事了。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#15$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將幼獸抱在臂彎裡，潔西卡順著它的皮毛輕輕撫摸。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒做任何事，只是慢慢等待著幼獸的哀鳴漸漸微弱，直至徹底消失。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#2$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我救不了它，但我至少……能讓它在一個溫暖的懷抱裡離開。", "name": "潔西卡"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傭兵做臨終關懷？我還是第一次見。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#2$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我能把它放在這裡嗎，老先生？我想……那頭母獸作為獵物來講已經夠大了。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼？還要我再幫你把它埋了，然後舉行葬禮嗎？", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，冬天林子裡的動物都飢腸轆轆的，留在這裡……說不定也能讓它們飽餐一頓。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是心腸軟不錯……但也不會因此什麼事都搞不清。", "name": "潔西卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_1034_jesca2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你搞得清楚，那就跟緊吧，傭兵小姐，你應該也不想在林子裡再迷一次路。", "name": "年老的獵人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1034_1#10$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風把霧氣吹散了……邁爾斯先生，您讓我們停下就是為了在這裡看一眼達維鎮嗎？", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1038_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……年輕時，我就喜歡跑到地塊附近的高地上，看看自己生活的鎮子到底是個什麼模樣。", "name": "邁爾斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1038_1#8$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時它是什麼樣的？", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1038_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熱鬧些、光鮮些……更有生命力些。", "name": "邁爾斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1038_1#9$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1038_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現如今……唉，回不到從前了……回不到了。", "name": "邁爾斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1038_1#7$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶……真的好冷啊。原來……我們的目標地點是這個樣子啊。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#9$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "芙蘭卡……", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想什麼呢？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是……突然又想到潔西卡。", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想什麼？你又不擔心她。", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我在想我們剛剛說的“機會”。", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#3$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，你說那個“讓她看清自己的機會”？", "name": "芙蘭卡"}, "figure_art": "avg_106_franka_1#1$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，終有一天……那個機會也會像陣風一樣吹過，或許會很冷，會讓潔西卡在風中狠狠打哆嗦。", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#3$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是那些在她眼前的迷霧也會被風捲走，在她前方的一切都會變得很清晰。", "name": "羅拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_4105_almond_1#2$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願她看到的……不會是我們眼前的景象。", "name": "雷蛇"}, "figure_art": "avg_107_liskam_1#3$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "42_i01", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "42_i01", "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 15.0}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "散開的霧氣中，由斷木殘枝組成的巨大轍痕順著山坡蜿蜒向下，一直延伸到谷地中央。"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盡頭處是一片擱淺的地塊。"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然相隔甚遠，但所有人都能看見，在地塊中心，一座高聳入雲的能源塔正有氣無力地噴吐著白息。"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如垂危的病人那般，艱難喘息。"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}